{"id":4680,"date":"2019-04-09T12:19:06","date_gmt":"2019-04-09T16:19:06","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/staging.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/une-autre-belle-initiative-verte-pour-le-cegep-de-saint-laurent\/"},"modified":"2023-06-14T13:20:11","modified_gmt":"2023-06-14T17:20:11","slug":"une-autre-belle-initiative-verte-pour-le-cegep-de-saint-laurent","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/nouvelle\/une-autre-belle-initiative-verte-pour-le-cegep-de-saint-laurent\/","title":{"rendered":"Une autre belle initiative verte pour le c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent!"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Le c\u00e9gep de Saint-Laurent atteint le niveau Excellence de la certification C\u00e9gep Vert du Qu\u00e9bec depuis 2008, soit plus de 10 ans. En ayant \u00e0 c\u0153ur de continuellement en faire plus sur le plan \u00e9coresponsable, le C\u00e9gep recycle, entre autres, ses objets \u00e9lectroniques. Qu&rsquo;ils soient d\u00e9suets ou bris\u00e9s, les ordinateurs, \u00e9crans et autres mat\u00e9riels \u00e9lectroniques peuvent \u00eatre r\u00e9cup\u00e9r\u00e9s de fa\u00e7on \u00e9thique et responsable.<\/p>\n<p>Depuis le d\u00e9but de l&rsquo;ann\u00e9e scolaire 2018-2019, c&rsquo;est plus de <strong>3 756 kg d&rsquo;objets \u00e9lectroniques qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9 recycl\u00e9s<\/strong>! Cela \u00e9quivaut \u00e0 environ 1 709 litres d&rsquo;essence et 5 tonnes de CO2 qui ont \u00e9t\u00e9\u00a0d\u00e9tourn\u00e9 des sites d&rsquo;enfouissement!<\/p>\n<p>Michel Rondeau, animateur \u00e0 la vie spirituelle et \u00e0 l&rsquo;environnement, tient d&rsquo;ailleurs \u00e0 remercier toute l&rsquo;\u00e9quipe des approvisionnements pour avoir coordonn\u00e9 cette initiative qui fait une vraie diff\u00e9rence!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>En 2018, plus de 3 756 kg d&rsquo;objets \u00e9lectroniques ont \u00e9t\u00e9 recycl\u00e9s de fa\u00e7on \u00e9thique et responsable par le C\u00e9gep!<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":3,"featured_media":4681,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[15],"sujet-actualite":[194,197],"etiquette-interne":[2256,2305],"class_list":["post-4680","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-nouvelle","sujet-actualite-environnement","sujet-actualite-institutionnel","etiquette-interne-environnement","etiquette-interne-institutionnel"],"acf":[],"publishpress_future_action":{"enabled":false,"date":"2026-05-05 21:35:19","action":"change-status","newStatus":"draft","terms":[],"taxonomy":"category"},"publishpress_future_workflow_manual_trigger":{"enabledWorkflows":[]},"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4680","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=4680"}],"version-history":[{"count":1,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4680\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":4947,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/4680\/revisions\/4947"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/4681"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=4680"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=4680"},{"taxonomy":"sujet-actualite","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/sujet-actualite?post=4680"},{"taxonomy":"etiquette-interne","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.cegepsl.qc.ca\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/etiq